verse.lines:
{lang-eng}We come to Him, our Priest and Apostle,
Clothed in His glory and bearing His name.
Laying our lives with gladness before Him;
Filled with His Spirit we worship the King.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}O Holy One, our hearts do adore You;
Thrilled with Your goodness, we give You our praise.
Angels in light with worship surround Him,
Jesus, our Savior, forever the same.{/lang-eng}
